title: EU's Juncker slams 'unacceptable' U.S. tariffs
text:
EU's Juncker slams 'unacceptable' U.S. tariffs Thursday, May 31, 2018 - 00:40
European Commission President Jean-Claude Juncker says the EU will take counter-measures after the U.S. decided to no longer exempt the bloc from steel and aluminum tariffs. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
